  "title": "Assistant Supervisor at LEARNING KIDZ(Tampines Junction))",
  "description": "<p><strong>SALARY will depend on :</strong></p>\n<p>1) no. of years of experience in this childcare industry</p>\n<p><u><strong>POSITION:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervisor Role or Assistant Supervisor Role depending on the years of experience</li>\n  <li>Located in Tampines (walking distance to Mrt)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mentor a team of teachers, highlight their strengths and provide regular feedbacks for professional development.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate and work closely with parents and teachers to address children's learning needs.</li>\n  <li>Respond to parents' enquiries and feedbacks</li>\n  <li>Well acquaint with ECDA CMS through children enrollement and subsidy applications</li>\n  <li>Aligned Centre's standards and quality with SPARKS requirement</li>\n  <li>Licensing </li>\n  <li>To lead a team and report to the centre director/manager</li>\n  <li>To suport managment team </li>\n  <li>To be independent and to work closely with the management</li>\n  <li>To be active in enrollment of children</li>\n  <li>Conduct frequent meetings with teachers</li>\n  <li>Passionate, Responsible and Bubbly</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>BENEFITS</strong></u></p>\n<p>Annual Leave, Performance Bonus, Monthly Incentives Payout, Healthy Fit Awards etc....</p>\n<p>Salary will depends on the years of experience in the sector</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>QUALIFICATIONS:</strong></u></p>\n<p>Leadership Certificate in early childhood</p>",
